3Ô∏è‚É£ Circuit Breaker Pattern (VERY HOT üî•)

  to prevent cascading failures
  tools: Resilence4j
  
  states:
  closed-normal
  Open - stop calls
  Half open - trial calls
  
  scenario:
  when notification service was down, circuit breaker opened so booking service continued
  without delays.
  
  is retring always good?
  no - retry storms can crash systems

